channel_info.title: Robbie Kramer
channel_info.description:
I'm Robbie Kramer 🎙Host of The Inner Confidence Podcast & Founder of Inner Confidence, Inc.

I lived an exhilarating single life filled with adventures and lessons, and ultimately achieved what I had always aspired to – finding an amazing, feminine, and loving wife. 

I believe my experiences provide a rare balance of wild freedom and committed love, equipping me with the insights to help you navigate the complexities of dating and relationships in today's world. Let me guide you to embrace your desires, improve your social prowess, and ultimately attract the partner who aligns with your highest aspirations.

You won’t find any fluffy, new-age, or cringy stuff here, just tested, proven and actionable advice that yields results.

Apply to join our exclusive Inner Confidence Community of ambitious men who are actively working together to achieve their goals faster   ► https://innerconfidence.com/community

You can email me at robbie@innerconfidence.com with any questions or comments.

transcription: {"text": "Hey guys, I'm Robbie. Welcome to the site. I want to teach you how to do something that most guys suck at. And most guys suck because they don't know what to do. That thing I'm talking about is how to attract an amazing girl that you don't know. Now, you may be social, you may have a lot of friends, a cool guy, that's how I used to be, but I didn't date the women I really wanted and the reason was simple. I didn't know what to do. I didn't know how to walk up to a woman in broad daylight or even in a bar and show her that amazing part of me that all of my friends knew, but I didn't know how to convey that side of me during the first impression. I didn't know how to approach. I didn't know what to say. I didn't know what to follow up, you know, the opening line with. I didn't know if she liked me or not. I couldn't read her signals and because I couldn't read her signals I didn't know when to go for the first kiss or when to make the move or when to ask for her number. I was clueless even though I was social. So if you're like me and you want to become a social genius, somebody who just sees it, they get it, they understand, they have the answers to all their questions when it comes to attracting a beautiful woman and making her your girlfriend or your wife or whatever you want, I will teach you how to do that. It's going to be fun and I really hope you enjoy the site and the resources I have to offer.
